Package: sgo
Title: Simple Geographical Operations (with OSGB36)
Version: 0.9.1
Authors@R: person("Carlos", "Lozano Ruiz", 
  email = "carloslozanoruiz@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/clozanoruiz/sgo
BugReports: https://github.com/clozanoruiz/sgo/issues
Language: en-GB
Description: A set of functions to help with spatial analysis mainly focused on 
  the OSGB36/ETRS89 transformation (Great Britain and the Isle of Man) by using 
  the Ordnance Survey's OSTN15/OSGM15 transformation model without any other 
  package dependency.
Depends:
  R (>= 3.4.0)
Suggests:
  sf,
  testthat (>= 3.0.0)
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
Copyright: OSTN transformation data included in this module is freely available
  from the Ordnance Survey but remains Crown Copyright (C) 2016 under the terms
  of the BSD licence.
Encoding: UTF-8
ByteCompile: yes
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Collate: 
  'sgo.R'
  'sgo_area.R'
  'sgo_bng.R'
  'sgo_distance.R'
  'sgo_laea.R'
  'sgo_ngr.R'
  'sgo_points.R'
  'sgo_set_gcs.R'
  'sgo_wgs84.R'
  'sgo_transform.R'
Config/testthat/edition: 3
